The inital code of translators.xiaomi.eu was pushed to github on 20 october 2013. Since that day a lot of things have changed. 
This file contains the most noteable changes over the years. For more details see the commits of this repository.

----------------------------------------------------
Year 2016 (version v16)
----------------------------------------------------
- Finetuned multi-processing
- Add index page generation for translators.xiaomi.eu (yes after almost 2 years)
- Redesigned check cycle (now only checking language if the language is changed)
- Rewritten apostrophe check

----------------------------------------------------
Year 2015 (version 5.x)
----------------------------------------------------
- New values check
- New variable check
- Doubles check for arrays and plurals
- Rewritten checks and caching (multi-processing support)
- Support for local_languages.xml
- Support for remote controller
- Support for MIUI7

----------------------------------------------------
Year 2014 (version 3.x / version 4.x)
----------------------------------------------------
- HTML updates 
- Introduce resources (MA-XML-CHECK-RESOURCES)
- Easy configureable languages
- New logfunctions (direct links to language repositories)
- Auto-detect new repositories
- Improved caching
- Introduce untranslateable check
- Multiple check modes (full / basic)
- Add MXCR system (preparsing of resources)
- Support for MIUI6
- Apostrophe check for arrays and plurals
- Add error count on logs

----------------------------------------------------
Year 2013 (version 1.x / version 2.x)
----------------------------------------------------
- Initial code
- Change logging from txt files into html 
- Support both server and local setups
- Introducuction of apostrophe error check
- Error categorization with colors
- Add double debug mode
